experiences.description:
• Being a proactive communication channel between upper management and clients;

• Taking part in the planning and executing process of engagements (ie. evaluate risks, determine scope of work and audit strategy, arrange teaming, assign and supervise tasks);

• Leading the audit team to perform audit procedures: Conducted plan on audit schedule, team mobilization and other relevant planning procedures; Delivered instructions on audit methodology; Monitored work progress and quality;

• Involving in the process of preparing financial statements of high-profile clients.

• Providing added-value to clients by sharing knowledge and consultancy over accounting regulations and accounting systems.

Client industries: Manufacturing, Telecommunication, Trading, Games.
